{"tid":215014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾 蔭 權 獲 准 保 釋","createTime":"2017-04-24T06:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T23:50:17.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43f94e2518f3af99d5e926244c346cb3713d1d93","tid":215014,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"高等法院今早處理前特首曾蔭權提出保釋外出等候上訴的申請，署理首席法官楊振權今午批准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n瀆職罪成被判囚20個月的曾蔭權，早前已入紙就定罪及刑期提出上訴，但其上訴申請仍未排期正審。現年72歲、已在赤柱監獄服刑兩個月的曾蔭權，兩周前因哮喘病發被送入瑪麗醫院羈留病房。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權所提出的上訴，涉及他本年2月被裁定罪成的藉公職作出不當行為罪，控罪指他於2010年1月1日至2012年6月30日期間，以特首及行會主席的身份參與決定雄濤廣播的數碼廣播牌照申請時，隱瞞他與雄濤主要股東黃楚標就深圳住宅進行商議。"},{"pid":"10004f2c0a8f8af1ab0eb6474f23667fa0b3c4bf","tid":215014,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a26d0601709768dccd604681ef5711d8e1b9b81","tid":215014,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"係我就快啲著草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def2fe1e1a58e512e46f259133e0b2f6a1caf093","tid":215014,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"689嬲到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c25fcf3c3b38555d89d8669c6e153a77b748c9","tid":215014,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594705f627ea8120e959044114e3d8d0b427c280","tid":215014,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為要坐到7月1"},{"pid":"a628b11f5dcd9558e930fb80bbd883aecf4d10cd","tid":215014,"uid":39141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0